\n搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b15e9f48785a73afc7484f8b15313da6a2f762","tid":2370884,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"空白頁可能因為 php 出錯, 同時 config 設定將 debug 模式設為關閉<br />\n所以你無辦法知發生咩事"},{"pid":"ffb56f297fb718e11c8ead104e678a573820e946","tid":2370884,"uid":11866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73b15e9f48785a73afc7484f8b15313da6a2f762","tid":2370884,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"空白頁可能因為 php 出錯, 同時 config 設定將 debug 模式設為關閉<br />\n所以你無辦法知發生咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"搞掂了！發現係要update d 插件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我發現佢個theme好多位都冇得轉字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪正常的"},{"pid":"2358934d92fd7cb39e50be669ba3292f5194ed20","tid":2370884,"uid":386390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffb56f297fb718e11c8ead104e678a573820e946","tid":2370884,"uid":11866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73b15e9f48785a73afc7484f8b15313da6a2f762","tid":2370884,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"空白頁可能因為 php 出錯, 同時 config 設定將 debug 模式設為關閉<br />\n所以你無辦法知發生咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"搞掂了！發現係要update d 插件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img